  "title": "Nurse/Scrub Nurse (OT-Orthopaedic)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Opto Systems (S) Pte Ltd</strong> is distributing Medical Devices (Spine Implants and Orthopaedics) to all hospital's in Singapore and Malaysia through its subsidiary Osteomed (M) Sdn Bhd.</p><p><br /></p><p>We are currently looking for:</p><p><strong>Nurse OR Scrub Nurse</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Manage the needs of the surgeons in OT and provide clinical support during surgeries, and be responsible for the product management in the assigned hospitals</li><li>Preparation of implants/instrument sets</li><li>Work with the sales team by receiving training and knowledge sharing</li><li>Collect competitive data and remain current on industry, customer, and competitive trends</li><li>Suitable training will be provided</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements :</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Nursing</li><li>Enrolled with Singapore Nursing Board</li><li>Relevant experience in Orthopedic will be an advantage</li></ul><p>Candidates with Medical Sales Experience will be an advantage. This is a replacement role.</p>",
